keep monthly payments low for a period of time when there is already substantial equity in the property jumbo home loans – an overview jumbo home loans are mortgages that are above the conforming lending limit currently  and up to  for highbalance conforming or that might not meet conventional lending guidelines jumbo home loans are often requested by our clients in higherpriced real estate markets such as los angeles and san francisco our staff has extensive experience in structuring and closing jumbo mortgages while still providing you with the highest levels of service you won’t find elsewhere what makes us the leaders in jumbo lending as a mortgage bank we underwrite and fund our own jumbo home loans to save you time and prevent the headaches that come with using an outside lender we provide flexible and competitive jumbo home loan packages with fixed or adjustablerate products as well as interestonly payment options our jumbo loans can also be used to purchase a second home or investment property experience the service you deserve secure no obligation expert advice i want toselectto buy a hometo refinance my current loan balanceto refinance and take cash outto get a second opinion i have a loan elsewhereto discuss something nonmortgage relatedwhere are you in the processi am under contractmaking an offeri need to get preapprovedwhat is your timeframe to buyless than one month months monthsdesired down paymentcash to take out mortgage balance value of home do you have an existing nd mortgage or helocyesnond mortgageheloc desired loan amountestimated purchase price purchase price how may we help youfirst namelast namephone numberemail address county californiaskype id optionalnamethis field is for validation purposes and should be left unchanged —  or  — call us today  by clicking on “contact me” you have agreed and accepted our terms and conditions and to do business electronically with carlyle financial had a great experience with carlyle financial i shopped ar